The result of this competition will be similar to the one between HDD and SSD.
While I like the sound of an engine, in terms of efficiency and acceleration, ICE cars simply can't win. Once we master renewable energy and energy density, EV will be the winner. The only down side is that I currently don't know how much an EV would cost to maintain on the long run, and there is no website that simply collects and shows how much people spend on their cars. If only...
